      "description": "2019 sedan in good condition. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 small surface scratches in a few spots, but no significant dents or paint damage. The interior is clean and functional, with light wear on high-contact surfaces. Mechanically sound with no known issues.",
      "price": 33000.0,
